        "collapsible_row_zVraUA": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does sizing work?",
            "icon": "lightning_bolt",
            "row_content": "<p>Note that there is a 'Size Chart' above that you should refer to for measurements of our appliances.<strong><br/></strong>- The R2 large is the same width as the R1 large but is a bit longer.  So if you were comfortable with the R1 large we recommend you get the R2 large size.<br/>- The R2 medium is a bit larger than the R1 small and so is good for adults with a smaller sized mouth. <br/>- The R2 does not currently come in a small size.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_wYPXBk": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is support?",
            "icon": "lightning_bolt",
            "row_content": "<p>When you purchase the 1-year support package you get access to:</p><ul><li>Our highly engaged Skool community of 3000+ members that are doing this process</li><li>Classroom of 60+ videos explaining how this works</li><li>A journal to track your progress, which Ken tracks and comments on a weekly basis on</li><li>Ability to DM Ken with your questions</li></ul><p>Watch this video for more information about support <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yPYIALdB0F8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yPYIALdB0F8</a></p>",
            "page": ""
